#

Sautéed Mushrooms with Garlic

20 min
$8.5
120 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Side Dish

Tags:

QuickEasyHealthySautéed

Description

Deliciously tender mushrooms sautéed with fragrant garlic, perfect as a side or topping!

Ingredients

  • mushrooms: 16 ounces
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • garlic, minced: 3 cloves
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • parsley, chopped (for garnish): 1 tablespoon
